import Mathlib
import Aesop

open Set

namespace Topology

variable {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]

/-- Three basic ‚Äúregularity‚Äìtype‚Äù properties of subsets of a topological space. -/
def P1 (A : Set X) : Prop := A ‚äÜ closure (interior A)
def P2 (A : Set X) : Prop := A ‚äÜ interior (closure (interior A))
def P3 (A : Set X) : Prop := A ‚äÜ interior (closure A)

/-- The *intersection* of two `P3` sets again satisfies `P3`. -/
theorem P3_inter {A B : Set X} (hA : P3 A) (hB : P3 B) : P3 (A ‚à© B) := by
  -- First, rewrite the goal in unfolded form.
  dsimp [P3] at hA hB ‚ä¢
  -- Take an arbitrary point of `A ‚à© B`.
  intro x hx
  rcases hx with ‚ü®hxA, hxB‚ü©
  -- Apply the `P3` property to each coordinate.
  have hx_intA : x ‚àà interior (closure A) := hA hxA
  have hx_intB : x ‚àà interior (closure B) := hB hxB
  -- The intersection of the two interiors is an open neighbourhood of `x`.
  have h_open : IsOpen (interior (closure A) ‚à© interior (closure B)) :=
    (isOpen_interior).inter isOpen_interior
  have hx_mem : x ‚àà interior (closure A) ‚à© interior (closure B) :=
    ‚ü®hx_intA, hx_intB‚ü©
  -- This neighbourhood is contained in the closure of `A ‚à© B`.
  have h_subset :
      interior (closure A) ‚à© interior (closure B) ‚äÜ closure (A ‚à© B) := by
    intro y hy
    rcases hy with ‚ü®hyA, hyB‚ü©
    have hy_clA : y ‚àà closure A := interior_subset hyA
    have hy_clB : y ‚àà closure B := interior_subset hyB
    -- A point in both closures lies in the closure of the intersection.
    have : y ‚àà closure (A ‚à© B) := by
      have h : closure A ‚à© closure B ‚äÜ closure (A ‚à© B) := by
        -- Standard topological lemma.
        exact closure_inter_subset_inter A B
      exact h ‚ü®hy_clA, hy_clB‚ü©
    exact this
  -- Turn the neighbourhood into an interior membership.
  have h_nhds : closure (A ‚à© B) ‚àà ùìù x :=
    Filter.mem_of_superset (h_open.mem_nhds hx_mem) h_subset
  exact (mem_interior_iff_mem_nhds).2 h_nhds

theorem interior_dense_iff {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    Dense (interior A) ‚Üî closure (interior A) = (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  simpa using (dense_iff_closure_eq (s := interior A))
